Jesús Tordesillas https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jes%C3%BAs_Tordesillas 0 Jesús Tordesillas (28 January 1893 – 24 March 1973) was a Spanish film actor. He appeared in 94 films between 1921 and 1973. He starred in the film Reckless which was entered into the 1951 Cannes Film Festival. Jesús_Tordesillas ( 28_January_1893 – 24_March_1973 ) was a_Spanish_film_actor .
